item.title: Agario game
item.description: Agario game is very simple in its content. Yes, and in terms of execution. And yet, somehow it attracts millions of players around the world?

item.title: Game Agario 3
item.description: A wonderful toy in order to take a little break from work and let your melting brains cool down. As in other games in the Agario series, the user needs to control the microorganism, devour everything nutritious and grow. There are a lot of other players around who are not averse to eating the one who is smaller. To catch up with the nimble little one, divide your cage into two.
